description: The grand finale to the first arc! Nocturnus and Galahad have finally found out who's been manipulating them, but have they cornered him--or has he cornered them?
name: Volume 8

description: Frank Hurt, an undercover agent for the Global Crime Task Force, is sent to infiltrate the criminal organization only known as The Syndicate Six. When his cover is blown and his life destroyed, he wakes up barely a man, his life changed forever. Within the depths of a massive secret facility, alien technology awaits, and a new life and mission for Frank -- revenge and the means to fulfill it.
name: Chapter Four

description: As his crusade against evil adults continues, Sam and his Giant take on more than they bargained for when a dangerous gang of bank robbers come to town. To survive, he'll have to depend on the one thing he can't trust; a grown up who knows the truth about Sam's Giant and the dangers lurking in the forest.
